<div style="padding: 10px 20px;">
	<h1>Hello <%= @user.name %></h1>
	<p>感谢您使用<strong style="color: #0084ff;">ReadTime</strong>.现在点击下方按钮链接进行密码修改:</p>
	<p>Thanks for your register At <strong style="color: #0084ff;">ReadTime</strong>. Now click on the link below to change your password:</p>
	<p>该链接将在2小时后失效.</p>
	<p>This link will expire in two hours.</p>
	<p>如果不是本人操作,请忽略这封邮件.</p>
	<p>If you did not request your password to be reset, please ignore this email and your password will stay as it is.</p>
	<p>
		<%= link_to  edit_password_reset_url(@user.reset_token,email: @user.email) do %>
			<button style="background-color: #0084ff;color: #fff;padding:10px;border-radius: 3px;cursor: pointer;font-size: 24px;">Reset Password</button>
		<% end %>
	</p>
</div>
